div.p:
When a speech of his in which he assailed Vindex was being read in the senate, at the words "the wretches will suffer punishment and will shortly meet the end which they deserve," all who were present cried out with one voice: "You will do it, Augustus."Of course used in a double sense. It also had not failed of notice that the last piece which he sang in
public was "Oedipus in Exile," and that he ended with the line:
Wife, father, mother drive me to my death.
